            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "ok, so it is UTF-8 encoding overlong sequences larger than `U+10FFFF` . some helper function in neovim consider these as printable, we need to change that to unprintable (so the GUI/TUI will recieve `<XX>` replacements instead)",
